  </div>
</div>


<div class="container">
	<div class="marketing">
		<h1>Introducing Classfuku</h1>
		<p class="marketing-byline">Inapproiate line involving the word "fuku".</p>
	</div>
</div>





<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
	  <div class="span4">
	  	<div><h3><center>We stay up late to answer your questions</center></h3></div>
	  	<p></br><center>"All" questions answered, and we mean it: if no one answers your question 6 hours after its posted, our <%= link_to "team", "#" %> will <b> personally look into your question and help you answer it. </b></center>
