	  <div class="span4">
	  	<div><h3><center>No dumb questions. No, really.</center></h3></div>
	  	<p></br></br><center>Classfuku is as anonymous as you choose to be, so you can focus on asking questions, and not worry about being judged on what you ask.</center>
	  </div>
	  <div class="span4">
	  	<div><h3><center>Your professor don't actually know about Classfuku</center></h3></div>
	  </br><p><center>Unlike <i>Blackboard</i> or <i>Piazza</i>, you (the students) run the content on Classfuku, not the professor.</center></p>
	  </div>
	</div>
